Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.

Homeschool RAYS
-
501100304
RAYS Homeschool Edition!
RAYS Homeschool program encompasses stroke development and condition training games and activities. Students must be 6-12 years of age to participate. Enrollment is by season, totaling 10 classes.
Each season is $65/student for City of St Cloud Residents, and $90/student for non-residents.
The student must be able to swim 2 full length of the pool (50yds) uninterrupted, complete a 30 second back float, and a 30 second water tread.
This program runs on Mondays 12:45pm - 2:15pm.
Student/parent cancellations will result in a forfeit of time - make-up classes will not be scheduled for lack of attendance.
In the event the class is cancelled due to weather, management will call/leave a message as soon as possible. This may be less than 15 minutes prior to class start.
Due to the unpredictability of Florida's weather, we are unable to offer rain checks or make-up lessons.
Please call 407-957-7136 for assistance.
